      "role": "user",
      "content": "Thanks, that's a good start. It's professional, but maybe a little bit too generic? I want to make sure he really feels how much we appreciated his time, so maybe we could add a sentence or two expressing how difficult the decision was for the team specifically? Can you make it sound a bit more personal and warm without losing the professional tone?",
      "source": "evaluator"
